OL,3,COctober is Black History Month, but is
OL,4,Cit time schools taught it all year
OL,5,Cround?
OL,7,FOctober 1 marked the start of Black
OL,8,FHistory Month, but campaigners calling
OL,9,Ffor a more inclusive education system
OL,10,Fsay the subject should not just be
OL,11,F"pigeon-holed" into just four weeks
OL,12,Fevery year.
OL,14,FThe teaching of black and ethnic-
OL,15,Fminority history is currently not a
OL,16,Fmandatory part of the school
OL,17,Fcurriculum.
OL,19,FThat's despite roughly 1 in 5 people
OL,20,Fin the UK identifying as being from a
OL,21,Fnon-white or mixed race background.
