OL,7,FIn 2022, the Welsh Government formally
OL,8,Frolled out their Black History
OL,9,FCurriculum, which they claimed would
OL,10,Fmake their children and young people
OL,11,F"more informed citizens".
OL,13,FTwo years into the new changes, St
OL,14,FPauls' Church School in Cardiff is
OL,15,Frunning a lesson on the black Welshmen
OL,16,Fand women who helped shape their
OL,17,Fmodern nation.
