OL,7,FPupils are split into groups and given
OL,8,Finformation on people like former
OL,9,FOlympic athlete Colin Jackson or Dame
OL,10,FShirley Bassey, and told to come up
OL,11,Fwith a pitch as to why they deserve
OL,12,Ftheir own statue.
OL,14,FGemma Maiorano is the school's
OL,15,FEquality, Diversity & Inclusion Lead.
